front.title: Royal Guard
front.gametext: Deploys only on Coruscant or to Emperor's site (or related site). When armed with a Force pike and defending a battle, adds one battle destiny. Emperor may not be targeted by weapons unless all Royal Guards present with Emperor are 'hit'.
front.lore: Member of Emperor's Royal Guard. Completely subservient. Royal Guards must fight one of their own to the death in order to complete their training.
